Tagline: Our Ruthless IPA With A Fiery Twist.
First brewed: 06/2016
Description:
Chili Hammer is the third of our super-charged hyped up hybrids. A smooth tongued spicy assassin. Chili and American hops unite for a flavour bigger than Texas. Citrus peel, mango, with a hint of spice on the nose. Delivers big grapefruit and mango with a smooth chili kick, followed by the bitterest of bitter finishes. Chili Hammer â€“ turn up the gas.

Food pairing:
[Aubergine and chickpea tagine, Firehouse chili con carne, Vanilla milkshake]

Brewers tips:
There are a multitude of chilies you can experiment with. Try the difference between Arbol and Habaneros.

